VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)@csrf_exempt
WHEN EXPR MISSING:@login_required|token_required|api_key|JWT|Bearer && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potentially insecure usage of Django's @csrf_exempt decorator.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Use of Django csrf_exempt Decorator.
